    },
    {
      "content": "This article helps you understand the options and make the right choice for your web application.",
      "pos": [
        754,
        851
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Azure App Service is the best choice for most web apps.",
      "pos": [
        853,
        908
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Deployment and management are integrated into the platform, sites can scale quickly to handle high traffic loads, and the built-in load balancing and traffic manager provide high availability.",
      "pos": [
        909,
        1101
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "You can move existing sites to Azure App Service easily with an <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>online migration tool<ept id=\"p1\">](https://www.migratetoazure.net/)</ept>, use an open-source app from the Web Application Gallery, or create a new site using the framework and tools of your choice.",
      "pos": [
        1102,
        1347
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>WebJobs<ept id=\"p1\">][]</ept> feature makes it easy to add background job processing to your App Service web app.",
      "pos": [
        1348,
        1447
